	<td>
		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Necromancer Quest</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><a href="mailto:">Aphrael Vesperia</a> | 
                        12/29/1999 1:39:40 AM</b></font></p>
			
			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">There are a great deal of new quests in the Temple that was just added.  The enterance is across the lava pit from Sol B.  I know for sure of the Necromancer quests in there.  You have to talk to a dark elf necro named Syllian (or something close).  She will tell you how to make Shadow Silk for 5pp and will also offer to make a Robe of Enshroudment, Shadowbound boots, and Shadowbound gloves for you if you bring her the components.  The components are as follows:  For the robe you need 1 large Shadow Silk, werebat wings from unrest, Mask of Shadows from a shadowed man, and a Globe of shadows from a Nokta shaman in guk.  For the Gloves you need 1 Inky Shadow Silk (she will teach you to make all the different typse of shadow silk), Septer of Sorrows (found at the circle-stair-waterfall in Guk  whatever that place is), and Skeletal Finger from the Giant Skele's in Rathe Mountains.  The Boots are no easier to get.  You need 1 regular Shadow Silk, Scepter of Tears (from Mistmoore), eye of shadow (from Shadowed men), and a skeletal toe from the same Gaint Skele's...  I hope this helps my fellow Necromancers out there and happy hunting!
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
			</p>
	</td>
		<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
		
