	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Update on above<BR>
I actually bothered paying the 5pp just to be sure (I know, I'm a sucker)<BR>
Shadow silk needs 1 shadow wolf pelt, 1 scroll of gather shadows and a silk swatch.<BR>
Large shadow silk is the same as Shadow silk, but with 2 pelts instead of one.<BR>
Inky shadow silk is the same as Shadow silk, but with an extra scroll of gather shadows.<BR>
<BR>
Shadow wolves can be found in EC, common to find a pelt on them and Gather Shadows can be found at any Necro guild.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
