			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have completed the quest for the Robe of Enshroudment, and here are the stats on it: +4 Int and +4 Agi, +5 SV vs Cold and Fire, AC 9.  Not bad at all really.  The items you need are of course the werebat wing found off the werebats in Unrest, a Mask of Shadow found from shadowmen (took a long time for me to find this one, actually), a Globe of Shadows found on the Nokta Shaman in Upper Guk (the spawn room is across the way from the ancient croc room), and Large Shadow Silk.  The robe is totally black and looks really good I think.  Hope that helps!
				</font>
